01:00:52.379 --> 01:00:57.500
right now and you said you have to ask a lot of questions from the stakeholders when they ask you

01:00:58.219 --> 01:01:03.260
how do you help them understand the difference between interesting questions just like keep on

01:01:03.260 --> 01:01:08.540
asking because you're the only data person they have to go to versus actually impactful

01:01:08.540 --> 01:01:11.500
while still maintaining that relationship with them

01:01:13.899 --> 01:01:19.580
yeah I would say that that's a challenge that I continue to build my skill set on I would say that

01:01:19.580 --> 01:01:26.540
