01:01:38.379 --> 01:01:43.100
I don't know maybe that's not the best way to go about it but kind of once I got to that point

01:01:43.100 --> 01:01:47.899
it's more about like having a conversation about an ask instead of it being transactional it's more

01:01:47.899 --> 01:01:55.100
like okay I understand that you wanted to look at this but actually you know like what's the why

01:01:55.179 --> 01:02:00.219
